	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />so my friend has a 40 inch lcd flat screen he hooked up his nes to with the av cables (yellow, white, red) through one of the ports in the back of the tv.  the games play fine, but there is a low humming sound.  is there any way to get rid of this?  i have mine hooked up like this and the sound is fine.

		

