	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I usually get a humming sound if the adapter is going bad, or isn't the correct one, this happens on my SMS because it's not the proper adapter. Have you tried using your adapter on his NES, or hooking your NES up to his LCD? Might help for some troubleshooting I think. I'm not a hardware guy, by the way, but my past experience in a console humming was because of the adapter used to plug in the system to the wall.

		

