	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I had the same issue with my NES when I was using a cheap thirdy-party AC power adapter.  Try a working Nintendo brand AC power adapter and see if that fixes the problem for you.  It fixed it for me.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
